The paper discusses a method to improve the robustness of deep learning models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method is inspired by the association and attention mechanisms of the human brain, which suggests a possible connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the potential application of the method to natural language processing (cs.CL), although this is not the main focus of the paper.
